}
if (!is_file('.idea/workspace.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: .idea/workspace.xml');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('.idea/workspace.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .idea/workspace.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') != '460d38ce679b06e62bc9fdedea9627173ce72698') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .idea/workspace.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea/workspace.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of .idea/workspace.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '460d38ce679b06e62bc9fdedea9627173ce72698') {
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '121f1338dfb9cd83596f3e9e5bf85cddefa44b24') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: .idea/workspace.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('.idea/workspace.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.idea/workspace.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.idea/workspace.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '460d38ce679b06e62bc9fdedea9627173ce72698') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .idea/workspace.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '3033e13a6d9f77ba41010cded46a7a4678cadaa0') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '3033e13a6d9f77ba41010cded46a7a4678cadaa0') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'bd91dc180a9c75e7d5bdc130059c375e996b2f5c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '3033e13a6d9f77ba41010cded46a7a4678cadaa0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') != '7f0afd1c8abf403cafbf7d70fee367437105b752') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') !== '7f0afd1c8abf403cafbf7d70fee367437105b752') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') !== 'f17fcbe4618244b344bb8467d92a9f1404ee7694') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') !== '7f0afd1c8abf403cafbf7d70fee367437105b752') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('phpstan.neon.dist')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: phpstan.neon.dist');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('phpstan.neon.dist')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): phpstan.neon.dist');
	} else if (sha1_file('phpstan.neon.dist') != '78ba339f4665093b4ed29ed4621707443972af0d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): phpstan.neon.dist');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('phpstan.neon.dist', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of phpstan.neon.dist');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('phpstan.neon.dist') !== '78ba339f4665093b4ed29ed4621707443972af0d') {
		if (@sha1_file('phpstan.neon.dist') !== '409bc86b1d1921bf14c7a95e32705c4af23cc9d4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: phpstan.neon.dist');
			$tmp = pathinfo('phpstan.neon.dist');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('phpstan.neon.dist')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('phpstan.neon.dist', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('phpstan.neon.dist') !== '78ba339f4665093b4ed29ed4621707443972af0d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): phpstan.neon.dist');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '19f9dc82e5292151df3443709dd84c78bf292ec2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '19f9dc82e5292151df3443709dd84c78bf292ec2') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '231918aa70aaa6a5c5237de36bd57e293bc02732') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '19f9dc82e5292151df3443709dd84c78bf292ec2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php');

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php') !== 'b71e295c4bfd922ca1139f2f7926e0924d43a0e5') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php');

		}
		writefile_19();

		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('LCAkc3RhdGljX2NvbnRlbnQsICRleHRyYV9oZWFkX3RhZ3MpOwoKT0lEcGx1czo6aW52b2tlX3NodXRkb3duKCk7CgplY2hvICRjb250Owo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/index.php');
	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/index.php') != '55bcadbb5248dd4670dda38076d856c5ad1e2a7a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '55bcadbb5248dd4670dda38076d856c5ad1e2a7a') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'dbb091f2ec0bd28f00e41ab3bc767bcdd70f39db') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '55bcadbb5248dd4670dda38076d856c5ad1e2a7a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('.version.php', "<?php // Revision 1143\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('.version.php')) !== '<?php // Revision 1143') err('Could not write to .version.php!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
